### Construction

Construction of this project began in 10 June 2018 and was completed in 23 October 2018. This was endymion's first project.

### Inspiration

The castle is inspired by Castello di Vignola in Italy. Tuscany served as inspiration for the region as well as the already existing material in neighbouring projects.
